{"tid":640780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：南生圍火警現場無找到助燃劑痕迹","createTime":"2018-04-24T13:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T14:53:08.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b24a1170713d94bd165644557f9fb433ff17950a","tid":640780,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南生圍接連遭縱火，包括本月初橫水渡設施被焚毀。警方向元朗區議會交代調查進展，指現場沒有找到助燃劑痕迹，有議員就要求政府收回南生圍的私人土地作保育。<br />\n<br />\n警方已向元朗地政處建議在政府土地上加裝閉路電視，又重申仍然積極調查案件，強調不會排除任何原因，亦已加強在南生圍巡邏。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303481&d=eGD4uhieo%2FJ1%2Ft8wCdr7FttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=17b79cd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303481&h=d9342264\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303481</a>"},{"pid":"a69dd98b6385e337d582324276966f0b07e4d87e","tid":640780,"uid":58086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"天氣乾燥，啲草又乾，使撚助燃劑咩"},{"pid":"5b19537dc175186248ca581e59588443b21cf564","tid":640780,"uid":1654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"傳真社影到有，姐係點"},{"pid":"97f9ae0c9beaf707661c46b8be6b07ad3e5c3f99","tid":640780,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571d63a88884ee16548418890222136861312dfd","tid":640780,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"講句搵唔到唔知可以收發展商幾多球呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}